{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_08_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 冬の朝の空に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next morning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9333333294,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、葵\n……って、何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Aoi.\n…Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.599999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.5539678097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲の振り付けのことなんだけど……\n進捗が、あまり良くなくてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About the choreography for the new song…\nIt’s… not going so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6207027316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日聞いた感じだと順調そうだったのに\n曲も出来てきてるし、コンセプトもまとまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounded like it was going smoothly when I asked you yesterday.\nThe song was coming along‚ and you had decided on a concept…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "うん。そこまでは良かったんだけど\nミクみたいな動きは、思ったより難しかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It was fine up to that point‚\nbut Miku’s movements were more difficult than I thought.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.199999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2370519161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けを大きく見せるちょっとしたコツはあるんだ\nそれを念頭に、四人で合わせてみたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are a few tricks to make the choreography look bigger.\nWe tried it out with the four of us‚ keeping those in mind‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央はまだなんとかなりそうだったけど\n愛とこころは、今回は明らかに練習時間が足らない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio seems like she’ll be alright‚\nbut Ai and Kokoro definitely don’t have enough practice time this time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.599999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.7341719787
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "二人は本番までになんとかするって言い張ったけど\n愛が無茶するから、昨夜はそこで切り上げたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They insisted that they’d manage by the actual performance‚\nbut I called it a night because I was worried Ai would overdo it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3863261064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、別にあの二人に怒ってる訳じゃないからね\nむしろ、無茶をやらせようとした僕が悪いんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ and I’m not angry at them or anything.\nIt’s my fault for trying to make them push themselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3333331744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.2209065597
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……ミクみたいな軽やかな動き、か\n言うは易く行うは難し、だなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… Miku’s light and smooth movements‚ huh?\nEasier said than done.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "コンセプトは悪くないと思ったけど、仕方ない\nみんなが起きてくるまでに別の案を考えるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought the concept was good‚ but it can’t be helped.\nI’ll think of another idea before everyone wakes up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.199999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.3765303452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……いいのか？\n昨日はあんなに楽しそうだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you sure?\nYou looked like you were having so much fun yesterday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.599999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "別に、ダンスの技術を自慢するのが目的じゃないからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not trying to show off my dancing skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2546481291,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8946479956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ミクの軽やかなダンスが、僕は本当に好きだったから\nあれを引き立たせられないのは残念だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really liked Miku’s light and smooth dancing‚\nso it’s a shame we can’t make it work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6666665077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.1922215938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、葵\nちょっと作業は一休みして、外に散歩に行かないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Aoi.\nDo you want to take a break from work and go for a walk outside?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.599999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "何？　何かいい案でもあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Do you have a good idea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5688204924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.7792966206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうじゃないけど、ずっと根を詰めてるみたいだからな\n息抜きしたら、きっとまたいい案が出るさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not really‚ but you seem to be racking your brains over it.\nso I thought a change of pace might help you come up with something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.0666665077,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-snow-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.333492299994,
          "startTime": 113.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0762127876
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0762127876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁー……夜のうちに一気に雪が積もったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… It snowed a lot overnight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.142878437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.5498379071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "大通りにずらっとビルが並んだ感じは東京と一緒だけど\n雪があるだけで、こうも風景が変わるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Odori Park with all the buildings lined up looks just like Tokyo‚\nbut the snow makes the scenery look so different.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.2446817412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ\nそれにしても……さ、寒い！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah.\nBut… it’s so c-cold!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6333311398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.1390442689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "気分転換しようって言ったのは君じゃないか\nその君が、真っ先に凍えてどうするんだか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the one who said we should go for a walk to clear our heads.\nWhat are you doing freezing up like that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7999978065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.5957107068
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば昨日の天気予報で\n最大級の寒波が到来って言ってた気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ I think the weather forecast yesterday\nsaid that a massive cold wave was coming…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8668871993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "なんだってそんな時に\nライブツアーの予定を組んじゃったのさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why did we schedule a live tour\nat a time like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.0333311398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.7407671452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、そんな先の天気までは分からなかったし……\nというか、葵は寒くないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I didn’t know what the weather would be like that far ahead…\nSpeaking of which‚ aren’t you cold‚ Aoi?",
